headline: I Shared a Bathroom With an Airbnb Host to Avoid NYC’s Hotel Prices
summary: CARRY ON BROOKLYN, N.Y.—I texted my roommate one morning last week to make sure the bathroom in the condo was free. “Is now an OK time to use the shower?’’ I thought my days of sharing bathrooms with strangers ended after college.
